                            <div>
                                <h3>
                                    How we use information we collect
                                </h3>
                                <p>
                                    We use the information we collect from all of our services to provide, maintain, protect and improve them, to develop new ones, and to protect CareerCircle and our users. We also use this information to offer you educational content more tailored for your upskilling specific needs.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    When you contact CareerCircle, we may keep a record of your communication to help solve any issues you might be facing. We may use your email address to inform you about our services, such as letting you know about upcoming changes or improvements, or with your permission, other notifications.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    We use information collected from cookies and other technologies, like pixel tags, to improve your user experience and the overall quality of our services. We may combine personal information from one service with information, including personal information, from other CareerCircle services – for example to make it easier to share things with people you know. We will ask for your consent before using information for a purpose other than those that are set out in this Privacy Notice.
                                </p>
                            </div>

                            <div>
                                <h4>
                                    Transparency and choice
                                </h4>
                                <p>
                                    You may contact us for any privacy related matters via email at <a href="mailto:privacy@CareerCircle.com">privacy@CareerCircle.com</a>.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    You may request information about any personal information we have stored about you and request that the information be removed by contacting us a <a href="mailto:privacy@CareerCircle.com">privacy@CareerCircle.com</a>, we will work with you to understand any data we store about you and remove it upon your request (requires identity verification).
                                </p>
